@miguelaferreira discussed with me the over-engineering wrapper method just to add 1 test and we agreed on getting rid of it for the following reasons:
1. It could lead other committers to add simple tests - like the one I added - and forget about the real tests that we need;
2. An experienced Software Engineer reviewing the code will spot problems with the string formats used.

I will retest the PR and post the results here.

Cheers,
Wilder

